metadata.name: Migrating - PLEASE READ
metadata.description:
The Degenz Access Pass is migrating to Degenz Code. Please see our pinned tweet on @DegenzNFT or this article for more information: https://mirror.xyz/osf.eth/GmrvX8eSMdEX3zYudwzHVQqH1aE8dhqM2X84FGjYixQ

Utility from these NFTs will be revoked after 31st December 2023.
